  Chok-chia2 su7-gian5 
  Chu7-iok 30 ni5 cheng5 goa2 bat giah8 pit lai5 sia2 siau2-soat “A-nia5 e5 Bak8-sai2” liau2-au7 chiu7 m7-bat koh giah8-pit sia2 siau2-soat. au7-lai5 bat thak8 tioh8 kou3 TeN7 Khe-phoan3 bok8-su tu3 e5 “Koe3 Si2-soaN3.” An2-ni i2-goa7, in-ui7 goa2 e5 gan2-kai3 eh8-eh8, na2-chun2 m7-bat koh thak8 tioh8 lan2 Tai5-oan5 kau3-kai3 koh chhut-pan2 chong-kau3 siau2-soat e5 khoan2. 
  Khiok bat chiap tioh8 phoe, a2-si7 tui3 lang5 tng-bin7 thiaN-kiN3 kong2 tui3 thak8 choat-tu3 “A-nia5 e5 bak8-sai2” lai5 siu7 an-ui3, sim7-chi3 jip8 sin3-giong2, a2-si7 sin3-giong2 khah chin3-pou7 e5 lang5. Che sit8-chai7 si7 i3-goa7 e5 siu-hek8. goan7 eng5-kng kui hou7 Chu2. Na7-si7 goa2 kau3 chit-si5 iau2 bo5 chu7-sin3 kong2 goa2 e7-hiau2 sia2 chong-kau3 siau2-soat. Si7 iau2-teh piN3 gin2-na2-hi3 na7-tiaN7. Goa2 e5 sim si7 teh pi7-pan7 chit8-phiN soat-kau3. Ia7 chiong hit-phiN soat-kau3 ka7 i kou3-su7-hoa3 (soat-kau3 kou3-su7-hoa3) an2-ni na7-tiaN7. Sou2-i2 un2-tang3 che7-che7 sou2-chai7 thak8 liau2 bo5 sim2-mih8 tu2-ho2. Che si7 tui3 sio2-ti7 e5 bo5 lau2-lian7. 
  Na7-si7 goa2 thong3-kam2 ti7 lan2 Tai5-oan5 e5 kau3-kai3 sit8-chai7 chin khiam3 chheh thang thak8. Tek8-piat8 ti7 hiong-chhoan, hai2-piN phian-phiah e5 kau3-hoe7, be7-hiau2 thak8 han3-bun5 e5 hiaN-che2 koh khah khiam3-eng7 ho2 e5 chheh thang hou7 in thak8. Chit pai2 khoaN3 IuN5 Sek8-lim5 sian-siN chu2-phian e5 “Oah8-mia7 e5 Bi2-niu5” chhut-si3, sio2-ti7 ui7-tioh8 i toa7-toa7 kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3. Goan7 Chu2 chiok-hok i e5 sin3, i e5 thiaN3 leng5-hun5, thiaN3 kau3-hoe7 e5 sim e7 jit8-jit8 tiong2-toa7. Sou2 choe3 e7 seng5-kong. 
  Lang5 m7-thang hi-hoa, khin5 iu2-kong, hi3 bu5-ek che si7 su7-sit8. Chong2-si7 koh chit8-bin7 gin2-na2 ai3 thiaN kong2 kou3-su7. Toa7 lang5 ai3 thiaN kou2, ai3 thak8 siau2-soat. Che ia7-si7 chit8-bin7 lang5 e5 chu7-jian5-seng3. In-ui7 ai3 thiaN sin5-ki5, hi2, nou7, ai, lok8 khut-khiok hu3 iu2 cheng5-kam2 e5 kou3-su7, hou7 lang5 e5 su-siuN2 u7 sin e5 chhi3-kek, che si7 lang5 e5 chu7-jian5. TaN lan2 chu7-jian5 bo5 chan3-seng5 Ki-tok-tou5 khi3 thak8 hih-hiauh sia5-im5 e5 chheh. Chong2-si7 boe7 thang bo5 poe5-iuN2 to7-li2, phin2-seng3 e5 chheh thang hou7 in thak8, lai5 lun7-tek8 in e5 seng-oah8. Tek8-piat8 ti7 bo5 eng5 tiong e5 phian3-khek, ti7 han5-ha5 bo5-liau5 tiong e5 si5, u7 si5 thang hou7 in tit-tioh8 sim-sin5 siong7 e5 an-ui3. Chu7-jian5 seng3-keng te7-it ho2, ki5-to2 te7-it ho2. Chong2-si7 u7-si5 lan2 na7 e7-tit ti7 koh-iuN7 e5 chu-bi7 tiong, chu7-jian5 iu5-goan5 si7 kin-ku3 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 “Seng3-keng” eng7 pat8-khoan2 e5 chu2-hoat, khah m7-si7 nge7-seng3 e5, u7 si5 eng7 nng2-seng3, khah sim-sek e5 kong2 hoat hou7 in chiah8, peN5-peN5 hou7 hoe7-iu2 tit-tioh8 leng5-seng3 e5 chin3-pou7, goa2 siong-sin3 ia7-si7 ho2. Chhin-chhiuN7 lan2 eng7 ho2 u7 li7-ek e5 “Tong5-oa7” gin2-na2 kou3-su7 hou7 gin2-na2 thiaN, lai5 chhoa7 in khah beng5-pek8 to7-li2. Siang7-si5 lan2 eng7 “Chong-kau3 siau2-soat” hou7 toa7 lang5 thak8, lai5 pang-chan7 in bat, ia7 hou7 in tit-tioh8 khah chhim-khek e5 ka3-si7, goa2 siuN7 ia7 bo5 m7-tioh8. 
  Chit-pai2 tit-tioh8 Tai5-oan5 Soan-to7-sia7 e5 IuN5 Sek8-lim5 sian-siN hoaN-hi2 chiong goa2 sou2 sia2 lan5-chhui3 kui2-te3 e5 toan2-phiN siau2-soat khioh choe3 chit8 pun2, choe3 tan-heng5 pun2 lai5 hoat-khan, ti7 chia chhim-chhim ka7 i seh-sia7. 
