  Cha2-ni5 tng tiong-kou2 se3-ki2 e5 si5, ti7 Au-chiu bou2 te7-hng u7 chit8 keng chin chong-giam5 bi2-le7 e5 siu-to7-iN7. IN7 au7 u7 chheng-san, cheng5-bin7 u7 lek8-sui2（au7 chheng-san, chian5 lek8-sui2）. Tng ti7 chhun-kong beng5-bi5 e5 si3-goah8-nih, hit e5 hong-keng2 sit8-chai7 tat8-tit lang5 e5 liu5-loan5. Chiau2-a2 ti7 chhiu7-ki hia chhiuN3, chia ho5. Bi2-le7 e5 ou5-tiap8 siang-siang tui3-tui3 poe ti7 hoe e5 tiong-kan. Ti7 chit e5 un-loan2 e5 chhun-kong, tai7-te7 e5 ban7-mih8 piau2-hian7 chit8-chiong2 e5 ho5-hai5. Chheng-lian5 ti3-sin ti7 hit tiong-kan, bi7-bian2 chhiok-keng2 seng-cheng5, tui3 lai7-sim e5 chhim-chhu3, chau2-chhut chit8 khoan2 bok8-beng5 ki5-biau7 e5 iau-kiu5, thou2-khui3, chit8-chiong2 tian5-bian5 e5 siong2-bong7, chit8-chiong2 ai3 e5 iau-kiu5. 
  Ui7 sim2-mih8 lan2 thai2 e7 the5-khi2 chit-keng si7-iN7, ia7 soa3 lian5-siong2 kau3 chit e5 chhun-thiN. Koh siuN7 kau3 hoe-khui chiau2-a2 thi5 e5 keng2-ti3, i2-kip8 chheng-lian5 un-loan2 ai3-cheng5 e5 bin5-bang7 nih8? Chiu7-si7 in-ui7 ti7 cha2-ni5 ti7 hit keng si7-iN7, ti7 bou2-ni5 e5 chhun-thiN u7 hoat-seng chit8-chan5 hou7 lan2 thiaN liau2 be7 kim3-tit kam2-than3 oan2-sek  e5 kou3-su7. Goan5-lai5 hit-keng si7-iN7 mia5 kio3-choe3 Seng3 Pi2-tek siu-to7-iN7. Hit tiong-kan u7 che7-che7 siu-to7-su7, tiong-kan chit8 e5 kio3-choe3 Pek8-sek Hui-kek8. Si7 chit8 e5 seng3-kiat sun5-sian7 e5 chheng-lian5. Hit-jit8 tng i teh siong7-thok8 ki5-to2-bun5 e5 si5, an3-chiau3 si7-iN7 e5 pan7-hoat, ti7 jit8-loan2 hong-ho5 e5 jit8, chiu7 siu-to7-su7 tai7-ke pai5-liat8, lai5 kiaN5-iu5 ti7 hoe-hng5-nih8, na2 kiaN5 na2 khoaN3 Siong7-te3 sou2 chhong3-cho7 toa7 chu7-jian5 e5 bi2-biau7, siang7-si5 tai7-ke kiong-chhiong3 to2-bun5 tang5-siaN chan3-bi2 Sin5 chu5-ai3 e5 ui2-tai7. Ti7 chit jit8 Pek8-sek ia7 kap tang5-phoaN7 saN-kap pai5-liat8, toe3 tai7-ke na2-kiaN5 na2 chhiong3 ki5-to2-bun5. Tu2 liam7 kau3 77 chat e5 si5, chai7-lai5 peN5 thaN2-thaN2 chhin-chhiuN7 kiaN3 e5 chui2-bin7, hut-jian5 hou7 chit8-liap8 sio2-chioh8-a2 kek-khi2 chui2-pho-hun5 e5 khoan2-sit. Koe3-khi3 Pek8-sek e5 sim si7 peng5-cheng7, chit8-tiam2-a2 to bo5 jiau2-tong7--e5. Ho2 chhin-chhiuN7 peng5-cheng7 e5 ou5-chui2, hut-jian5 hou7 chit8-boe2 sio2-hi5-a2 thiau3-tong7. Ti7 i i2-keng theng5-tiam7 bo5-hiang2 e5 sim-hian5-siong7（theng5-chi2 put-beng5 e5 sim-hian5-siong7）, ho2 chhin-chhiuN7 hut-jian5 hou7 chit8 e5 lang5 ka7 i toaN5 tan5 chit8 siaN e5 khoan2. 
  Pek8-sek si7 chit8 e5 chin iong2 chin toa7-han3, sin-the2 kiong5-chong3 e5 chheng-lian5, u7 lat8, ji5-chhiaN2 un-nga2 kho2-ai3. Na7 kong2-khi2 i e5 lat8, u7 chit8-pai2 hit keng si7-iN7 e5 hong-tiong7 ti7 poaN3-lou7 poah8-to2, siong tioh8 kha-kut be7 kiaN5. Pek8-sek eng7 siang-chhiu2 ka7 i pho7 khi2--lai5, soa3 chu7 an2-ni ka7 i pho7 kau3 chhu3. Kau3 ui7 i e5 bin7 bo5 pian3-sek, bo5 chhoan2, sit8-chai7 chin u7 lat8. Ji5-chhiaN2 i si7 chit8 e5 bin7-iong5 chun3-bi2 chheng-siu3 e5 lang5. I e5 bak8-chiu hian2-beng5 koat-toan3-lat8, kap tong5-cheng5-sim. Si7 chit8 e5 kam2-cheng5 hong-hu3, cheng3-tit8 ji5-chhiaN2 sun5-kiat e5 bi2 lam5-chu2. 
  TaN tauh-ti2 hit-si5 si7 sim2-mih8 lai5 phah-loan7 Pek8-sek e5 sim nih8? Goan5-lai5 chit e5 hoe-hng5 u7 chit8 cho7 chhiuN5. Ia7 hoe-hng5 lai7 u7 chit8-ui7 tek8-piat8 khah koan5 e5 sou2-chai7, na2-chun2 lun-a2 e5 khoan2-sit, lang5 na7 khia7 ti7 chit sou2-chai7 e7-tit khoaN3 iN7 lai7-goa7 e5 keng2-ti3. Pek8-sek seN-tit toa7-han3, che ia7 be7-tit koe3-chek i, sin-chhai5 khoe-ui2 si7 Sin5 sou2 siuN2-su3--e5. Tu2-tu2 i kiaN5 kau3 lun-a2 teng2 e5 si5, che ia7-si7 be7-tit koe3-chek i, chiaN5 chhau3-tu2-kham2, i tu2 kiaN5 kau3 hia, bak8-chiu khoaN3 tui3 chhiuN5-a2-goa7 chhut-khi3, m7-kin2 ia7 m7-ban7, tu2-tu2-ho2 khi3 khoaN3 tioh8 chit8 e5 chin-sui2 e5 lu2-chu2 kiaN5 tui3 iN7-goa7 koe3, che ia7 be7-tit koe3-chek-tit--i. Na2-li2 e7 hiah chhau3-khiau2, hit-si5 chit e5 sui2 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 e5 choan5 iong5-mau7 the2-thai3 e7 chau2-jip8 i e5 bak8-chiu. Che si7 in-ui7 cheng5 chit8 me5 u7 choe3 toa7 hong-thai, chhiuN5-piN e5 toa7-chhiu7 tng7 chit8 oe toa7-oe chhiu7-ki, siang3 tui3 chhiuN5-nih8 loh8-khi3, chhiuN5 to2 chit8-khiah. Hit e5 sio2-chia2 e5 sin-chhai5 tu2-tu2 ti7 hia chhut-hian7. Sou2-i2 it-bok8 liau2-jian5, khoaN3-tit chin chheng-chho2. Che long2 be7-tit koe3-chek sim2-mih8 lang5, peng7 m7-si7 sim2-mih8 lang5 e5 chho3-gou7. Chit e5 sio2-chia2 tauh-ti2 ho7 choe3 sim2-mih8 mia5, m7-si7 pat8-lang5 chiu7-si7 Sia7-bun5 Ma2-li7 sio2-chia2. I tak8-jit8 to chiau3 le7 tui3 hia koe3, tui3 in a-chek e5 chhan5-chng khi3 kau3 A-ma2 e5 tau khoaN3 A-ma2. Jian5-au7 chiah koh to3-khi3 a-chek e5 tau. Tak8-jit8 an2-ni lai5, khi3 keng-koe3 hit-keng si7-iN7 e5 goa7-chhiuN5. Che ia7 m7-si7 chit-ui7 bi2-le7 e5 sio2-chia2 thiau-ti5 kou3-i3 beh lai5 in2-iu2 chit e5 siu-to7-su7. I pun2 si7 bo5 i3-su3 lai5 keng2 kiaN5 chit tiau5 lou7. 
  Sio2-chia2 pun2-lai5 si7 chit8 e5 chin keng3-khian5 e5 lu2-chu2. I chu7-se3 chiu7 sit-loh8 pe7-bo2, put-tek-i2 ti7 A-chek tau kia3 toa7. I si7 chit8 e5 kou-khou2 chek8-bok8 sim u7 kong2 be7-chhut e5 sim-bun7 e5 lang5. I si7 tui3 sin3-giong2, tui3 Siong7-te3 lai5 tit-tioh8 i5-it e5 an-ui3. Chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni siok-tek keng3-khian5 e5 lu2-chu2, na2-li2 e7 thiau-ti5 keng2 chit tiau5 lou7 lai5 in2-iu2 Siong7-te3 thiau-ti5 keng2-tiau3 sin5-seng3 sun5-kiat e5 siu-to7-su7 leh? Na7-si7 hit chit8 jit8 i tui3 hia koe3, hiah tu2-ho2 taN-thau5 khoaN3 tui3 chhiuN5-lai7 e5 hoe-hng5, khoaN3 tioh8 koan5-koan5 e5 lun-a2-teng2 u7 chit8 e5 siu-to7-su7, kan-ta chit8 e5 ti7 hia kiaN5-lai5 kiaN5-khi3. I ia7 houN3-ki5-sim khia7 teh ka7 i khoaN3, sio2-chia2 e5 sim-lai7 sit8-chai7 si7 teh siuN7 kho2-keng3 ah! Hit ui7 siu-to7-su7 un2-tang3 si7 chin sin5-seng3 sun5-kiat, goa2 eng3-kai ia7 tioh8 chhin-chhiuN7 i u7 hit ho7 seng3-sun5 e5 sim-su chiah ho2. Na7-si7 tng i an2-ni siuN7 e5 si5, siang7-si5 sim-lai7 ia7 soa3 na2-chun2 u7 hou7 chit8-tiam2 sim2-mih8 jiau2-tong7 e5 khoan2-sit. I kak-tit hit ui7 seN-choe3 khoe-ui2 e5 lang5 kap i pun2-sin sui-jian5 si7 saN-li7, ji5-chhiaN2 tiong-ng u7 chhiuN5 keh-teh, sui-jian5 chit8 e5 si7 ti7 chhiuN5-lai7, chit8 e5 si7 ti7 chhiuN5-goa7. chong2-si7 ti7 put-ti put-kak e5 tiong-kan na2-chun2 u7 hoat-seng chit8-khoan2 bok8-beng5 ki5-biau7 saN-lian5 chhin-chhiat e5 sim-cheng5. 
  Te7-ji7-jit8 tui3 hia keng-koe3 e5 si5, i kou3-i3 oaN7 pat8-tiau5 lou7, bian2-tit koh tui3 si7-iN7 e5 piN-a2 keng-koe3. Na7-si7 chin ki5-koai3, ho2 chhin-chhiuN7 u7 chit8 khoan2 e5 lek8-liong7 ti7 i e5 lai7-bin7 teh hoan2-khong3, na2-chun2 hou7 i put-tek-put tioh8 chiau3 ku7 tui3 si7-iN7 koe3 chiah e7-eng7-tit e5 khoan2-sit. Mui2-jit8 kiaN5-koe3 si7-iN7 e5 si5, i long2 e7-tit khoaN3-kiN3 i (siu-to7-su7) ka-ti7 chit8 lang5 khia7 ti7 hit e5 koan5 lun-a2 e5 sou2-chai7. I sim-lai7 soa3 put-ti put-kak oh8 liam7 khi2 siu-to7-su7 sou2 liam7 e5 ki5-to2-bun5. Ti7 chheng-cha2 e5 si5 bo5 tiuN-ti5 i soa3 e7-hiau2 liam7 cha2-khi2-si5 e5 ki5-to2-bun5, ia7 ti7 hong7-hun e5 si5, i ia7 put-ti put-kak liam7 khi2 si7-iN7 thong-iong7 e5 ki5-to2-bun5. I soa3 ho2 chhin-chhiuN7 pian3-chiaN5 choe3 i (siu-to7-su7) liam7 ki5-to2-bun5 siang7-ho2 e5 tang5-phoaN7 lah. U7-tang-si5-a2 poaN3-mi5 teh khun3 ti7 chhng5-nih8, hou7 chhu3-goa7 e5 kau2 teh pui7 e5 siaN, pui7 kiaN chheN2 e5 si5, i e5 sim-lai7 ia7 sim-bun7 kong2 chit-si5 hit e5 siu-to7-su7 poh-kaN2 iau2-teh ki5-to2 leh, i ia7 chiu7 sim-tiong khian5-seng5 ki5-to2 khi2-lai5. 
  Ma2-li7 seN-choe3 kek-tong7 jin5-sim e5 sui2, na7-si7 tang-chin kong2 keh-chhiuN5, koh keh chhau2-pou, kiam2 chin-chiaN3 khoaN3 i e5 bin7 khoaN3 e7 chheng-chho2, che si7 chit8 e5 bun7-te5? M7-ku2 na7 khoaN3 i chin-sui2 chheng-siu3 e5 the2-thai3, kiaN5-lou7 ho2 khoaN3, i khin-khin e5 kha-pou7-siaN, kap i seN-seng5 leng7-goa7 u7 chit8-khoan2 phiau-jian5 e5 hong-tou7, che bo5-gi5 tak8-pai2 to e7-tit khoaN3 chin beng5. chong2 kong2 Pek8-sek mui2-jit8 to am3-am3 ki3-tit sio2-chia2 tui3 hia koe3 e5 si5-khek. Kau3 hit e5 si5 na7 kau3, i m7-chai an2-choaN2 chu7-jian5 ji5-jian5 chiu7 ng3 iN7-goa7 liau5-bang7. Hit-si5 chiu7 ia7 chu7-jian5 e7 khoaN3 tioh8 Ma2-li7 ti7 hng7-hng7 tui3-bin7 e5 soaN-pho teh loh8--lai5. U7 si5 hou7 chhiu7-ki jia-chah8-leh, be7-tit khoaN3-kiN3 i e5 choan5-sin, na7-si7 it-teng7 kau3 chit8 e5 si5, tng i oat-koe3 soaN-pho bin7 ng3 si7-iN7 teh kiaN5--lai5 e5 si5, i thang khoaN3-kiN3 chit8-pak kek8 bi2-le7 e5 tou5 chit8-iuN7, chiu7-si7 chit8-ui7 kek8 iu-nga2 bi2-le7 e5 lu2-chu2 ti7 i e5 bin7-cheng5. I khoaN3-kiN3 i e5 si5, sim keng3-ka keng3-khian5, keng3 kak-tit sim-keng2 e5 chong5-ko sun5-kiat, i ka-tit i ho2 chhin-chhiuN7 thiN-sai3 e5 chit8 e5, put-tek-put hou7 i seN-chhut khian5-seng5 kiong-keng3 e5 sim. Tng i tak8-jit8 hng7-hng7 khoaN3-kiN3 i e5 si5, to hou7 i kam2-kak na2-chun2 thiN u7 li7 i (siu-to7-su7) khah kin7 e5 khoan2-sit. 
  Na7-si7 Pek8-sek ka-ti7 liah8-choe3 che si7 m7 eng3-kai. I siuN7 kong2 i ka-ti7 chho3-lah, i kam2-kak ka-ti7 i2-keng si7 piN3 choe3 chit8 e5 ka2-mou7 ui5-sian7 e5 lang5 lah. I liah8-choe3 sim-lai7 che-iuN7 su-liam7 tioh8 chit e5 sio2-chia2, it-teng7 si7 chit8-hang7 be7-tit thang sia3-bian2 e5 choe7-koa3. Tui3 an2-ni i chiu7 ka-poe7 khek-khou2 thok8-keng ki5-to2, ka-tiong5 kim3-chiah8 e5 chhu3-sou3 kap si5-kan. Tui3 an2-ni i e5 bin7 chit8-jit8 chit8-jit8 tit8-tit8 khah siau-san2 loh8-khi3. I e5 bak8-chiu chit8-jit8 chit8-jit8 khah thap loh8-khi3. In-ui7 siuN7 beh chiong i sim-bak8 tiong bi2-le7 e5 ngou2-siong7 koaN2 chhut-khi3. I chiu3-choa7 m7 koh peh khi3 hit e5 lun-a2-teng2, bian2-tit koh bang7 tui3 goa7-bin7 khi3. I chun2-pi7 chin-chiaN3 beh chiong i e5 sim koaiN ti7 chit e5 siu-to7-iN7 e5 chiah8-chhiuN5-a2 lai7. I m7-goan7 koh hou7 se3-siong7 e5 iu2-hek8, chiong i koh thoa chhut-khi3. I tang-chin chhut-lat8 kiaN5 chit e5 chiu3-choa7, chin7-lat8 sit8-heng5 bo5 koh peh-chiuN7 chit e5 lun-a2-teng2. M7-kaN2 koh ng3 hit e5 chhiuN5-a2-khiah hia kiaN5, kiaN-liau2 ban7-it na7 koh khoaN3 tioh8 hit e5 bi2-lu2, tui3 an2-ni e7 hou7 i keng3-ka khah san2 loh8--khi3, e7 piN3 na2 m7 chiaN5 lang5 e5 khoan2. 
